## Official Arch packages

<% packages.official.sort(sortPackages).forEach(function(package){ -%>
- <%- `[${package.label}](${package.url}): ${package.description}${package.source_url ? ` [Source](${package.source_url})` : ''}` %>
<% }); -%>

