## Hardware

<% packages.hardware.forEach(function(machine){ -%>
### <%- machine.name %>

<% machine.packages.forEach(function(package){ -%>
- <%- `[${package.label}](${package.url}): ${package.description}${package.source_url ? ` [Source](${package.source_url})` : ''}` %>
<% }); -%>
<% }); -%>

## Available aliases

For a list off all available aliases, [read more here](./ALIASES.md) or run `aliases` after installation

## Firefox plugins

- [Linkclump for Firefox](https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/linkclump-for-firefox): Lets you open, copy or bookmark multiple links at the same time

<% browserPlugins.firefox.categories.forEach(function(category){ -%>
### <%- category.label %> (Firefox)

<% category.plugins.sort(sortBrowserPlugins).forEach(function(plugin){ -%>
- [<%- plugin.name %>](<%- browserPlugins.firefox.url %>/<%- plugin.id %>): <%- plugin.description %>
<% plugin.extra.sort(sortBrowserPlugins).forEach(function(extra){ -%>
  - [<%- extra.name %>](<%- extra.url || `${browserPlugins.firefox.url}/${extra.id}` %>): <%- extra.description %>
<% }); -%>
<% }); %>
<% }); -%>
